            },
            {
               "text": "<p><table id=\"yupana0\" class=\"tawapukllay\"><tr><th colspan=\"4\"><i>Yupana</i></th><th>Valores</th><th>Resultado</th><th>Movimientos</th></tr> <tr id=\"tf1\"><td id=\"tc1f1\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f1\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f1\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f1\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f1\"><span id=\"vl1\"></span> x <span id=\"vr1\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f1\">&nbsp;</td><td id=\"tc7f1\" rowspan=\"5\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf2\"><td id=\"tc1f2\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f2\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f2\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f2\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f2\"><span id=\"vl2\"></span> x <span id=\"vr2\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f2\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf3\"><td id=\"tc1f3\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f3\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f3\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f3\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f3\"><span id=\"vl3\"></span> x <span id=\"vr3\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f3\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf4\"><td id=\"tc1f4\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f4\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f4\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f4\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f4\"><span id=\"vl4\"></span> x <span id=\"vr4\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f4\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf5\"><td id=\"tc1f5\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f5\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f5\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f5\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f5\"><span id=\"vl5\"></span> x <span id=\"vr5\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f5\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "El tablero posee cuatro columnas por cinco líneas que representan la Yupana: La primera columna contiene cinco círculos; La segunda posee tres círculos; La tercera tiene dos círculos; La última presenta solo un círculo. Este patrón se repite en todas las líneas. Junto a la Yupana, añadimos dos columnas que muestran los números que usamos convencionalmente. Finalmente, incluimos una columna que describe todas las etapas de suma realizadas para obtener el resultado de la multiplicación.",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><b>Tabla 1</b>: Representación de la <i>Yupana</i> según Poma de Ayala (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('a62b520a-f443-4d83-ab51-b99c9a46dab8'); return false;\">Prem, Dhavit, pp. 355, <htdate0></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('f5b74f18-0bc4-46d2-8a5c-64dd80b74dd1'); return false;\">Poma de Ayala, Felipe Guaman, pp. 361 - 362, <htdate1></a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
